because they wanted to live.

07:14.400 --> 07:15.697
Now, why would he do that?

07:15.760 --> 07:17.489
Because by fighting
to stay alive,

07:17.570 --> 07:20.095
they used up resources
that he thought
were better used

07:20.170 --> 07:21.660
on healthier patients.

07:21.740 --> 07:23.605
You make him sound like
an actuary.

07:23.670 --> 07:24.932
Hmm.

07:25.010 --> 07:27.205
Most people think life
is priceless.

07:27.280 --> 07:28.338
Not Klepper.

07:28.410 --> 07:31.140
He did a cost-benefit analysis
on these people,

07:31.210 --> 07:33.519
figured that the cost
outweighed the benefits,

07:33.580 --> 07:35.810
and killed them
because of it.

07:35.880 --> 07:37.984
KLEPPER:
You killed someone.

07:38.050 --> 07:40.883
