believe you belong in prison.

07:40.960 --> 07:42.313
Their belief is based

07:42.390 --> 07:45.052
on a Judeo-Christian
tradition of justice.

07:45.130 --> 07:46.859
Mine is more algebraic.

07:46.930 --> 07:49.899
There's a constant
and a variable.

07:49.970 --> 07:51.460
The constant
is the work you do.

07:51.530 --> 07:53.066
It has value,

07:53.140 --> 07:55.199
and it will be compromised
with you behind bars.

07:55.270 --> 07:58.535
The variable
is what economists
call the VSL,

07:58.610 --> 08:01.329
the value
of statistical life.

08:01.410 --> 08:03.298
In this case,
the value of your life

08:03.380 --> 08:05.200
versus the value of the life
of the witness

08:05.280 --> 08:09.046
whose testimony
will put you behind bars.

08:09.120 --> 08:11.418
Okay, I can make it
worth their while
not to say anything.

08:11.490 --> 08:13.253
